## HTML Task to know usage of basic tags.

1. Fix the bugs in below snippet

```HTML
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Document
            <body>
                guvi
        </title>
    </head>
    <div>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
        <div>
            <div>
                Guvi Geek Network
            </div>
        </body>
    </html>
```
Solution:

<html lang="en">
   <head>
       <title>Document
          
               guvi
       </title>
   </head>
   <body>
   <div>
       Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
       <div>
           <div>
              Guvi Geek Network
           </div>
       </body>
   </html>
 

